name: Personal Financier
body:
### Welcome to the homepage of PersonalFinancier.

The aim of this project is to create the best value for money personal finance package available.   A package that allows every household the opportunity to understand and manage their finances easily.  Watch this space!

After your page is generated, you can check out the new branch:

```
$ cd your_repo_root/repo_name
$ git fetch origin
$ git checkout gh-pages
```
tagline: Understanding your personal finances with ease.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
